channel.title: [NEW RELEASE] xXericXx's 508 IP Changer Client! [ NEW RELEASE]
channel.description:
[[url=http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?mwnlnuyajmq/]Download Client Now![/url]]
Hey all!
Well here is my first release on my own 508 IP Changing Client :]! One thing is, I havn't taked any pictures simply because it's just a very simple client. Click Run, type in the IP Address of the server, and that's it! So, ya know. :]
[u]Here's some brief instructions on how to use the client:[/u]
[b]1. Download WinRAR (If you havn't got it already): [url=http://www.rarlab.com/download.htm/]Click Here[/url] 2. Download the Client: [url=http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?mwnlnuyajmq/]Click Here[/url] 3. Extract the Client to your Desktop. 4. Open the extracted file. 5. Click, "Run Client." 6. Type in the IP Address of the server you want to play. 7. Your Done! Simple as that :].[/b]
Please leave your comments about the client such as, do you like it? Does it need any fixing? Should I make a v2? Stuff similar to that. Thank you for viewing this post!
Please enjoy the client, if you have any questions feel free to add my MSN: dontaskme_askher@live.com. MSN is the best way to contact me, I'm signed on ALOT. So, :].
- xXericXx
